message.body: So Michael can't get off. August is a very busy month for him. Do I doubt think we can go. I'm sorry: (
I know. It sucks. But you and Mike can use the alone time.
Are you able to go out to do something today? I get home from work around four.
I'm actually headed to the beach with my sister for the day. We probably won't be going on the beach cause it's rainy and gross but we'll go on the boardwalk.
But WE need to do something!!! I went out for brunch with Sam last Sunday and I felt like I was cheating on you! Haha. Jk but you know what I mean!
I haven't seen everyone in a looooong time. I do want to see everyone
I know. Well try for next weekend.
